  "text": "Although DR6 is expressed highly in many cancer types, its role and underlying molecular mechanisms in cancer progression remain unclear. It has been found previously that DR6 level in the serum increases in patients with late-stage OVCA [CITATION_1] . Through analysis of TCGA database, we also identified DR6 overexpression in OVCA. Therefore, we aimed to investigate the function of DR6 in OVCA.",
